    <item>
      <title>DoorDash 业绩未能给华尔街留下深刻印象，股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/doordash-orders-beat-estimates-as-new-categories-lure-users</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管 DoorDash Inc. 发布了稳健的第四季度收益报告，但周五该公司股价仍创下近两年来的最大跌幅。尽管华尔街并没有对这一结果真正挑剔，但分析师指出，该股最近的上涨设定了很高的标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/doordash-orders-beat-estimates-as-new-categories-lure-users</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 21:06:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
